Detailed Description

Processor that provides Ahc2 prototype calibration information to other processors.

To obtain the object in other processors use: Ahc2CalibrationsProcessor::getCalibrations( "Ahc2SiPMCalibrations processor name" )

processor parameters

steering file parameter name

description

MappingProcessorName

name of the mapping processor that provides the necessary Mapper class

MipConstantCollection

name of the MIP constants collection

MipSlopesCollection

name of the MIP slopes collection

GainConstantCollection

name of the gain constants collection

GainSlopeCollection

name of the gain slopes collection

PedestalCollection

name of the pedestal collection

SaturationParametersCollection

name of the saturation parameters collection

TimeSlopesParametersCollection

name of the timeslopes parameters collection

TimePedParametersCollection

name of the time pedestal parameters collection</tr

PixelScaleFactorsCollection

name of the pixel scale factors collection

GlobalPixelScaleFactor

global value for the pixel scale factor

CellQualityCollection

name of the saturation collection
